  "title": "Manager, Loan Operations",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 1063944]</strong><br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee daily treasury and loan operations, ensuring timely and accurate settlements in line with internal controls and SLAs.</li><li>Supervise SWIFT message processing and system management.</li><li>Ensure compliance with SOPs, regulatory standards, and operational risk controls.</li><li>Validate and reconcile trade and settlement data across treasury and loan products.</li><li>Drive process improvements, system enhancements, and new product implementations.</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams, counterparties, and clearing houses to resolve settlement or payment issues.</li><li>Support management with reports, audits, and ad-hoc projects.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>6 years of experience in international banking, covering treasury operations and/or wholesale loans.</li><li>Strong understanding of fund finance, structured or corporate finance, and loan products (SBLC/LC).</li><li>Proficient in SWIFT, Excel, and banking systems; detail-oriented with strong control awareness.</li><li>Knowledge of FX, Money Market, Bonds, and Derivatives is an advantage.</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.<br /><br />Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/<br /><br />EA Personnel Name: Ong Kang Quan Ryan<br />EA Personnel Registration Number: R23116952<br />EA License No.: 07C5771</p>",
